* $\\sphericalangle CGF = \\sphericalangle EGH = 180^{\\circ} − 60^{\\circ} − (60^{\\circ} − \\alpha + \\beta) = 60^{\\circ} + \\alpha - \\beta$.

Tātad $\\sphericalangle CGF = \\sphericalangle EGH = 60^{\\circ} + \\alpha − \\beta$.

